                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a href="http://www.google.com/reader/preview/*/feed/http://blog.timothyfisher.com/?feed=rss2" title="Subscribe in Google Reader"><img src="http://blog.timothyfisher.com/wp-content/themes/fadtastic_theme/images/subscribe/googleread2.jpg" alt="Subscribe in Google Reader" width="91" height="17" /></a>
